ei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">美国</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">DARPA</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">项目</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">,\r\n	BioMagnetICs Program, 2003/1-2005/1, 130</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">万美元，第二负责人</span></span></span></span> \r\n		</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0.29in;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"western\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><b>有突出代表性的科研成果：</b></span></span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-indent:0.29in;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">1. </span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">在美国</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">Intel</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">公司工作期间，作为研发团队带头人研发了世界上最先进的</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">14nm</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">及</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">10nm</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">芯片制造工艺检测及功能检测技术，在设计及制备基于</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">MEMS</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">的高密度、高电流强度、高机械性能探针阵列（超过</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">20</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">万根探针）技术上实现了突破性创新，为</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">Intel</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">最新的两代芯片产品在摩尔定律的时间节点上实现量产做出了杰出贡献。个人获得</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">Intel</span></span><span><span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">公司研发总部颁发的技术开发质量奖</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">，团队荣获</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">Intel</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">（</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">ATTD</span></span><span><span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">）部门颁发的技术创新杰出贡献奖</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">。</span></span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-indent:0.29in;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">2. </span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">在美国国家同步辐射研究中心</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">CAMD</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">工作期间，作为技术第一负责人参与了美国军方</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">DARPA</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">资助的将巨磁电阻传感器用于生物检测的</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">BioMagnetICs</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">项目。个人以第一作者在美国电子工程师协会</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">(IEEE)</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">的期刊</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><i>Journal\r\nof\r\nMEMS</i></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">发表论文，首次提出了在低温下制备多层三维结构的微流体系统的工艺，并实现了与巨磁电阻传感器的大规模集成。由于该工艺与传感器表面生化改性的工艺兼容，因而促成了项目合作伙伴</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">NVE</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">公司在团队的研究成果基础上开发生产新型巨磁电阻生物传感器产品。</span></span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-indent:0.29in;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">3. </span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">以第一作者及通信作者发表在</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><i>Sensors\r\n&amp; Actuators </i></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">等杂志的系列论文从理论及实验上探索了仿生多级非对称微纳复合结构在化学传感器上的应用。该系列论文对设计及制备仿生高灵敏度及高选择性的气体传感器及环境监测传感器具有重要的指导意义，被在</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><i>Nature</i></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">上发表过同主题文章的同行多次引用。同时被授权微纳复合仿生结构的制备专利两项。</span></span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-indent:0.29in;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">4. </span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">以通信作者发表在美国化学协会的期刊</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><i>ACS\r\nNano</i></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">的论文建设性的提出了将微米／纳米复合结构与量子点集成实现多维度复杂能源器件的概念，并创新应用于基于光电化学的水分解器件，进而报道了远超目前国际报道同类器件最高水平的能量转换效率。</span></span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-indent:0.25in;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">5. </span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">与中国外籍院士王中林教授共同发表在美国化学协会的期刊</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><i>Analytical\r\nChemistry</i></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">的论文利用交流介电电泳（</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">AC-DEP</span></span><span><span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">）效应对微流体中的纳米线进行高精度的批量组装</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">，并在此基础上制备出基于纳米线的光电传感器。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">同时在实现动态操控纳米线的基础上提出了研究纳米材料力学性质的新思路及新手段。</span></span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-indent:0.29in;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">6. </span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">在博士论文中首次提出并实现了高通量高精度操控微流体中微纳粒子的芯片实验室（</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">Lab\r\non a\r\nChip</span></span><span><span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">），并在此基础上研发出</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">基于磁泳和负介电电泳的生物分子镊阵列。该工作在美国新发行期刊</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><i>Technology</i></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">发表后随即被</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">Science\r\nDaily</span></span><span><span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">等</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">多家美国媒体</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">报道，称该技术因为提供了高通量分析</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">生物单分子的</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">手段而加速了生命科学领域重要大分子的研究进展，并探索以前无法涉足的生命科学问题。</span></span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-indent:0.29in;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">7. </span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">在硕士论文里首次提出箔片气体轴承极限承载能力的数学模型并推导出解析解；而且对气体轴承的动态气压及热流分析提出了全新的三维仿真。该原创性工作已被写入由著名摩擦学家</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:14px;\">Ri